obtains the e5-square for the bishop.[%csl Ge5]}) 36. c7 {[%cal Gf2f4]} e5 37.
Be7 $1 Rhc8 38. Rd6+ {An attempt to win a drawish position which eventually
led to a loss.} ({White had to agree with a draw after} 38. Rxb5+ Ke6 (38...
